description: After participating in the Kanto, Orange Islands and Johto Leagues, http://anidb.net/ch6693 [Ash] decides to begin anew in yet another journey; this time by himself and http://anidb.net/ch8091 [Pikachu], in the land of Hoenn. Though he isn`t alone for long, as 10 year old http://anidb.net/ch23585 [May] (who dislikes Pokmon but wants to come along to see the world) travels with him after Pikachu destroys her bicycle. Ash also meets up with his old companion, http://anidb.net/ch16390 [Brock], and May`s younger brother, http://anidb.net/ch23586 [Max]. Together, they travel along in Hoenn, battling Gym Leaders, entering Contests, and other events on the way to the Hoenn League.

SPECIAL.description: Dr. Yung, an enigmatic Pokmon scientist, has developed a new Mirage system that uses computer data to resurrect extinct Pokmon, like Kabutops and Armaldo. Professor Oak, Ash and his companions show up at the Mirage Mansion at Dr. Yung`s invitation, and watch a demonstration of the machine`s capabilities. In the middle of a battle between Dr. Yung`s Mirage Pokmon and Ash, the machine goes haywire and a Mirage Aerodactyl swoops in and kidnaps Dr. Yung. A man calling himself "The Mirage Master" appears and announces to everyone that the Mirage System can be used to create Pokmon with absolutely no weaknesses. Ash, Misty, and Professor Oak struggle to stop the madman and escape with their lives.
